@startuml sequence-pengaturan-petshop
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Sequence Diagram — Pengaturan Bisnis Petshop (Owner)

actor Owner
participant "Aplikasi Web\n(Admin)" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

Owner -> App : Buka /admin/pengaturan
App -> API : GET pengaturan (auth owner)
API -> DB : SELECT pengaturan_petshop
DB --> API : row atau fallback .env
API --> App : Form pengaturan terisi
App --> Owner : Tampilkan form (peta, antar-jemput, bank, promo, WA)

Owner -> App : Submit perubahan
App -> API : POST /admin/pengaturan (CSRF)
API -> API : Validasi field
alt Valid
  API -> DB : UPSERT pengaturan_petshop
  API -> API : clearCache AppSettingsService
  API --> App : success flash
  App --> Owner : Redirect form + pesan sukses
else Tidak valid
  API --> App : errors per field
  App --> Owner : Form dengan pesan error
end

note over Owner, DB
  Perubahan hanya memengaruhi estimasi & booking baru.
  Booking lama tetap memakai snapshot jarak/biaya.
end note

@enduml
